Heat Beat Celtics, Grizzlies Down Thunder in NBA Playoff 2nd Round Openers

-- B y   D e x   M c L u s k e y
-- 
2011-05-01T22:19:43Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-01/heat-beat-celtics-grizzlies-down-thunder-in-nba-playoff-2nd-round-openers.html
The  Miami Heat  beat the Boston Celtics
99-90 in the opening game of their National Basketball
Association second-round playoff series.  Also today, the Memphis Grizzlies logged a 114-101 win at
the Oklahoma City Thunder in Game 1 of their Western Conference
playoff series.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dex McLuskey at 
 dmcluskey@bloomberg.net  